in photosynthesis changes.

252
00:13:23,750 --> 00:13:27,390
And so if we do the same
thing, mimicking high light,

253
00:13:27,390 --> 00:13:29,900
what we see is a change
in our distribution

254
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:32,390
and an increase in
the level of energy

