492
00:24:10,890 --> 00:24:14,550
And I hope that we can use
this integrative approach

493
00:24:14,550 --> 00:24:18,130
to tackle this very
simple, very complex,

494
00:24:18,130 --> 00:24:21,180
mechanistic problem in a
way that we can hopefully

495
00:24:21,180 --> 00:24:25,140
advance food security and
ultimately human health.

496
