940
00:44:54,650 --> 00:44:57,020
not only at the molecular
level, but all the way

941
00:44:57,020 --> 00:45:00,030
to the global biosphere
level, the oceans.

942
00:45:00,030 --> 00:45:02,850
Which you can do with
this simple little cell.

943
00:45:02,850 --> 00:45:05,810
And some of the things-- these
