982
00:46:55,860 --> 00:46:58,490
There are thousands
of different species

983
00:46:58,490 --> 00:47:00,465
are making these
vesicles in the oceans

984
00:47:00,465 --> 00:47:01,590
and putting them out there.

985
00:47:01,590 --> 00:47:07,180
It's like dissolved information
going around in the oceans.

986
00:47:07,180 --> 00:47:10,280
And also studying interactions
between prochlorococcus

987
00:47:10,280 --> 00:47:14,317
and other organisms, a
new evolutionary theory

988
00:47:14,317 --> 00:47:14,900
was developed.

989
00:47:14,900 --> 00:47:16,940
Not in my lab, but
in a colleague's lab,

990
00:47:16,940 --> 00:47:18,750
called the Black
Queen Hypothesis,

991
00:47:18,750 --> 00:47:22,200
which is really interesting.

992
00:47:22,200 --> 00:47:25,390
So some people say, well,
that's all very interesting.

993
00:47:25,390 --> 00:47:27,850
It's basic research,
